headline: How the Cigna Deal Talks Are Shaping Humana’s 2025 Value Outlook
summary: Thinking about what to do with Humana stock right now? You are not alone. Healthcare stocks have been on a bit of a rollercoaster, and Humana has been no exception. Over the past month, the stock has jumped more than 27%, with a solid 30% gain over 90 days. Numbers like that tend to catch investors' attention.
